history.content:
I am interested in conducting research about the possibility of using Machine Learning to enhance web autofill function. More specifically, I wondered if it is possible to establish a model and predict the behavior of a certain user on a time selector from a certain website.

Here are a few questions:

  • What are the possible platforms that I can find a dataset to train my model?
  • What actions should I take if there is no dataset that satisfies the requirement?
  • I have been reading articles on arvix.org. Apart from that and the school libraries, where can I find out about pre-established works and results?
  • Are there any workshops or other resources about how to maximally utilize the school library database to do research?
  • Is it possible to have someone supervise my work, or at least, provide some advice if I came across any problem?
history.subject: Questions about research
